Ebbro 43809 Toyota Supra (JZA80) 2006 Super GT Series GT500 Class 23rd Place A. Couto/K. Hiranaka/S. Ayari

Purchased: 2014
Manufacturer page: http://www.ebbro.jp/SHOP/43809.html

Andr√© Couto, Katsuyuki Hiranaka, & Soheil Ayari (round 6 only) raced for triple a Toyota Team SARD in the 2006 Super GT Series. 2006 was the last year the Supra was raced in the Super GT series and it raced along with it's replacement - the Lexus SC430. Their best result was a 9th place finish in Round 7 at Twin Ring Motegi. They finished the season in 23rd place, behind 4 other cars that only competed in round 6 (Suzuka 1000km) that season. But they sure looked good trying!
